E = EllipticCurve(label)\
j = E.j_invariant()            # returns an element of QQ\
\\end\{lstlisting\}\
\
References: $j$-invariant and the $b$-, $c$-invariants: \\cite[Section III.1]\{silverman:aec\}.\
Relation to CM: \\cite[Appendix A]\{silverman:advanced\}.\
