\\subsubsection*\{Column F: Root Number\}\
The root number $w \\in \\\{+1, -1\\\}$ is the sign in the functional equation of the L-function:\
$$\\Lambda(E, s) = w \\cdot \\Lambda(E, 2-s)$$\
where $\\Lambda(E,s) = N^\{s/2\}(2\\pi)^\{-s\}\\Gamma(s)L(E,s)$ is the completed L-function.\
